totalSupply.title: Token Supply
totalSupply.text1: At launch, Magnet DAO will have a Total Diluted Supply of 10,000,000 $MAG.

distribution.title: Distribution
distribution.text1: Magnet DAO will be selling 65% of the Total Diluted Supply at launch. Of the remaining 35% - 20% of tokens will be reserved for the team (locked and vested), 10% for marketing & partnerships, and 5% for initial liquidity providing.
distribution.text2: We will be posting a medium article with full details of our tokenomics and our launch in the coming days. Stay tuned!
